				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The frame counter loops.  So after it does those 4 (or 5) steps, it just keeps repeating them.<br /><br />The thing is there's several APU cycles (~3700) between each step of the frame counter.  So there are ~3700*(V+1) cycles between volume changes for the decay.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
						<tr valign="middle">
							<td class="gensmall" align="right">
							
